race.comment: Open race to close out the card. DAVIKAR (12) returned in good order with a solid Gold Coast victory before just missing the frame at the Sunny Coast last time out. Strips fitter third-up from the spell and looks the runner in this field with the most upside. Rates the testing material. CARDIOLOGIST (5) is two from two over this distance range and will be ready to peak now third run back. Top-three aspirations. TOOLATEMATE (9) goes well for hoop Thornton who has two wins and a placing from just four steers. In the mix. BLACK MINTO (10) is usually thereabouts and is a must for the multiples as is GLASS OF ROSE (16) who should be ready to show something third-up.
